Name: Naxos
About the game: Naxos is like all of my other games! I just feel like there arent many Auto Battle RPGS out there.... I really want to keep moving the genre forward! Okay why not try even more different formulas?? This time I decided to not use big menus ==( Many houses) I tried compacting everything in the game in 3 houses! I also feel like the game is better to learn... By making things small... Features: Craft equipment Almost Endless Grind*** Academy(Abbilites to learn) 10 Different Scenarios 10 Unique Enemies Automatic Progression Mining!
